{"tid":1258711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超聲波遙控警犬執行任務　北京申專利","createTime":"2019-06-26T08:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T05:35:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1976e5336d6318106c83b2ab5f7842d9a13a9b4d","tid":1258711,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2866028/org/2c55ab5e8934e2ff9c56b88216636f16.jpg/dj6QVWwPTwE0aD2VLBQspFkwFhRFvjur_LqUYvy6lGI?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2866028%2Forg%2F2c55ab5e8934e2ff9c56b88216636f16.jpg%2Fdj6QVWwPTwE0aD2VLBQspFkwFhRFvjur_LqUYvy6lGI%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=368688f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京公安公交總隊的警犬現場表演執行任務。（北京公安）<br />\n<br />\n超聲波控制 無聲指揮警犬<br />\n<br />\n據介紹，北京警方還研究出超聲波遠距指揮警犬的方法。由於警犬聽到的音頻範圍要超出人類，因此他們想到用超聲波指揮警犬，就可以解決在遠距離、不驚動疑犯的情況下，無聲控制警犬完成特定任務。警方指出，這種利用遙控器發射超聲波指揮警犬的方法，已向國家專利局申報專利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2866029/org/a415625bf21beea24efb04eb9120b682.jpg/gFLbLYGn8fZm8CzLHDARJ8Swe6RQLh_4qnIcWqpyHFo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2866029%2Forg%2Fa415625bf21beea24efb04eb9120b682.jpg%2FgFLbLYGn8fZm8CzLHDARJ8Swe6RQLh_4qnIcWqpyHFo&h=db50330e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/335830/%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E8%B6%85%E8%81%B2%E6%B3%A2%E9%81%99%E6%8E%A7%E8%AD%A6%E7%8A%AC%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%94%B3%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9#media_id=2866029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F335830%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%2581%2599%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%258A%25AC%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258B%2599-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25